data.text: @Kel_a_c Oh what an exciting life we now lead. The highlight of the day going for a vaccination. A walk up the road and meet anyone of a similar age and the conversation soon turns to 'have you had your vaccination yet'? Damn you #COVID.

@pagechord Great news Alan pleased Mrs R booked in as well ❤️
It’s the way only way out of this situation ✌🏻

@lynnroylesmith Many I know have suffered either mild or really upsetting side effects. I've been sat waiting but so far so good. Mrs R just wants to get it over with. Glad it went alright for you Lynn.
@pagechord Had mine yesterday too. AZ. No side effects. I was pleasantly surprised as I’m in group 5. Very happy.
